						<summary>

						<p>Records gift of 4 <hi rend="italic">puṭṭis</hi> of land irrigated under a certain tank for two perpetual lamps, for food offering and for <hi rend="italic">āchārya-bhōgam</hi> in the temple of Sōmēśvara in <hi rend="bold">Maṟucheṟvu</hi> in <hi rend="bold">Sārakināṇḍu,</hi> by <hi rend="bold">Chōḍagaṅgadēva's</hi> son-in-law, with the permission of that king.</p>						

						<p>First Side.</p>						

